{"tree":{"type":"node","kind":"SOURCE_FILE","width":29,"children":[{"type":"node","kind":"LET_BINDING","width":20,"children":[{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"let","width":3},{"type":"token","kind":"WHITESPACE","text":" ","width":1},{"type":"node","kind":"ERROR","width":0,"children":[]},{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"{","width":1},{"type":"token","kind":"WHITESPACE","text":" ","width":1},{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"x","width":1},{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":";","width":1},{"type":"token","kind":"WHITESPACE","text":" ","width":1},{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"y","width":1},{"type":"token","kind":"WHITESPACE","text":" ","width":1},{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"}","width":1},{"type":"token","kind":"WHITESPACE","text":" ","width":1},{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"=","width":1},{"type":"token","kind":"WHITESPACE","text":" ","width":1},{"type":"node","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","width":5,"children":[{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"point","width":5}]}]},{"type":"token","kind":"WHITESPACE","text":"\n","width":1},{"type":"node","kind":"ERROR","width":2,"children":[{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"in","width":2}]},{"type":"token","kind":"WHITESPACE","text":" ","width":1},{"type":"node","kind":"ERROR","width":1,"children":[{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"x","width":1}]},{"type":"token","kind":"WHITESPACE","text":" ","width":1},{"type":"node","kind":"ERROR","width":1,"children":[{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"+","width":1}]},{"type":"token","kind":"WHITESPACE","text":"\n","width":1},{"type":"node","kind":"ERROR","width":1,"children":[{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"y","width":1}]}]},"diagnostics":[{"kind":{"id":"E0007","name":"invalid-pattern","expected":"identifier or pattern","found":{"kind":"{","text":"{"},"fix":"add a variable name, \"_\" (underscore) to ignore it.","hint":"\nThe left side of a let-expression allows you to pattern match on values to assign them to variables, but also to deconstruct them and access their inner values.\n\n   ```ocaml\n   let variable = 42 in\n   let { x; _ } = point in\n   let Some x = optional in\n   (* ... *)\n   ```\n\nBeware that pattern matching on only one of many possible values will lead to runtime errors!\n"},"span":{"start":3,"end":3}},{"kind":{"id":"E0003","name":"missing-let-binding-equals","expected":"=","found":{"kind":"{","text":"{"},"fix":"add = between the pattern and expression","hint":"Every let binding needs an = between the pattern and the expression."},"span":{"start":3,"end":3}},{"kind":{"id":"E0005","name":"unexpected-structure-item","expected":"structure item (e.g., let, type, module)","found":{"kind":"keyword","text":"in"},"hint":"Structure items are top-level declarations like let, type, or module."},"span":{"start":23,"end":24}},{"kind":{"id":"E0005","name":"unexpected-structure-item","expected":"structure item (e.g., let, type, module)","found":{"kind":"identifier","text":"x"},"hint":"Structure items are top-level declarations like let, type, or module."},"span":{"start":25,"end":26}},{"kind":{"id":"E0005","name":"unexpected-structure-item","expected":"structure item (e.g., let, type, module)","found":{"kind":"+","text":"+"},"hint":"Structure items are top-level declarations like let, type, or module."},"span":{"start":27,"end":28}},{"kind":{"id":"E0005","name":"unexpected-structure-item","expected":"structure item (e.g., let, type, module)","found":{"kind":"identifier","text":"y"},"hint":"Structure items are top-level declarations like let, type, or module."},"span":{"start":29,"end":30}}]}
